OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773079565
OL,3,CCharity 'devastated' after food bank
OL,4,Cdestroyed by arsonist
OL,6,FA charity says it has suspended all of
OL,7,Fits projects after a suspected arson
OL,8,Fattack on its food bank.
OL,10,FBramwell's Hope's premises in
OL,11,FStaincliffe Road, Dewsbury, were
OL,12,Fdestroyed by fire in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Sunday.
OL,15,FFounder Tanisha Bramwell said: "I do
OL,16,Fnot have the words to fully express
OL,17,Fhow devastating this is.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773079565
OL,3,CCharity 'devastated' after food bank
OL,4,Cdestroyed by arsonist
OL,6,F"Not just for us, but for the families
OL,7,Fwho depend on us - the mothers who
OL,8,Fcome to us when they have nowhere else
OL,9,Fto turn, the children we feed, the
OL,10,Fpeople who rely on what we have built
OL,11,Ftogether in this community."
OL,13,FWest Yorkshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Fsaid two crews were called to the
OL,15,Fincident at 4.45am on Sunday.
OL,17,FThey managed to extinguish the blaze
OL,18,Fbefore it spread to a first floor flat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773079565
OL,3,CCharity 'devastated' after food bank
OL,4,Cdestroyed by arsonist
OL,6,F"This has been recorded as a suspected
OL,7,Fdeliberate ignition and passed to West
OL,8,FYorkshire Police," a spokesperson said.
OL,10,FBramwell's Hope, which was launched in
OL,11,F2020, runs youth projects and homeless
OL,12,Fsupport as well as a food bank.
OL,14,FIt said CCTV showed a lone individual,
OL,15,Fbelieved to be a male, approaching the
OL,16,Fbuilding before deliberately setting
OL,17,Ffire to the entrance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
