PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773079565
OL,3,CCharity 'devastated' after food bank
OL,4,Cdestroyed by arsonist
OL,6,FMs Bramwell said she had been the
OL,7,Fvictim of "online trolling" in recent
OL,8,Fweeks and was taking a "step back"
OL,9,Ffrom charity activity for
OL,10,F"safeguarding reasons".
OL,12,FShe added: "This has put me at risk,
OL,13,Fit's put my volunteers at risk, it's
OL,14,Fput my staff at risk, it's put the
OL,15,Ffamilies that live around this area at
OL,16,Frisk, and I cannot fathom why this has
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
