OL,3,CCharity 'devastated' after food bank
OL,4,Cdestroyed by arsonist
OL,6,FCharity trustee Jenny Holden-Stokes
OL,7,Fadded: "Our priority right now is the
OL,8,Fsafety of everyone who works at, uses
OL,9,For lives near the food bank so at
OL,10,Fpresent all our projects are on hold.
OL,12,F"It cannot be ruled out that this is a
OL,13,Ftargeted attack so we need to take
OL,14,Fevery precaution and follow advice
OL,15,Fgiven."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
